</gallery>ML97與ML99型分別於 1999 年 2 月 1 日和2000 年 7 月 3 日開始運營<ref name=":2" />，ML97與ML99延續ML90系列的外觀、技術，ML總共購買了 57 節ML97車廂，包括38節動力車與19節拖車；以及 114 節ML99車廂，包括76節動力車與38節拖車，二者均採用4動2拖的6節編組，或2動1拖的3節編組營運，列車最高速度72公里/小時，採用標準軌距、750伏特直流電第三軌供電。與ML90、ML95不同處在於，ML97與ML99型的車廂之間是相通的，藉此增加載客量，因此ML97與ML99型的動力車每節載客量可以達到165人，其中座位38人，站位127人；拖車每節載客量185人，其中座位44人，站位141人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Série 97|url=http://www.metrolisboa.pt/obras/equipamentos-e-sistemas/material-circulante/serie-97/|access-date=2022-02-08|work=www.metrolisboa.pt|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425035724/http://www.metrolisboa.pt/obras/equipamentos-e-sistemas/material-circulante/serie-97/|archive-date=2014-04-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Série 99|url=http://www.metrolisboa.pt/obras/equipamentos-e-sistemas/material-circulante/serie-99/|access-date=2022-02-08|work=www.metrolisboa.pt|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426020126/http://www.metrolisboa.pt/obras/equipamentos-e-sistemas/material-circulante/serie-99/#|archive-date=2014-04-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 營運 ==

=== 營運時間 ===
里斯本地鐵每天早上 6：30 至凌晨 1 點營運，但少數車站只營運到晚上 9：30，且在節假日關閉。各路線班距不一，藍、黃線平日尖峰班距4至5分鐘，離峰6至9分鐘，假日班距8至9分鐘，黃線平日早高峰至晚高峰間的離峰時段，以大坎波站為起訖站，分兩段營運，往市區方向班距5分50秒，往郊區班距11分40秒。綠線平日尖峰班距5分35秒，離峰6至12分鐘，假日班距8至9分鐘；紅線平日尖峰班距6分15秒，離峰和假日班距7至10分鐘。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Timetables and frequency|url=https://www.metrolisboa.pt/en/travel/timetables-and-frequency/|access-date=2022-02-08|work=Metropolitano de Lisboa, EPE - English|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508224739/https://www.metrolisboa.pt/en/travel/timetables-and-frequency%20/|archive-date=2021-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 票務 ===
里斯本地鐵車票分為單程票與定期票。最基本的單程票為60分鐘票，旅客可以持該票券無限次數搭乘里斯本公車、[[里斯本電車|里斯本電車]]，但只能搭乘里斯本地鐵一次，售價1.5[[欧元|歐元]]。除了60分鐘票外，旅客也可以購買24小時票，24小時票可以在時間內無限次數搭乘地鐵，票價依據搭配交通工具而有差異，最便宜的只能搭乘地鐵、[[有軌電車|有軌電車]]與公車，票價6.45歐元；地鐵、有軌電車與公車加上[[塔霍河|塔霍河]]的[[渡輪|渡輪]]票價9.6歐元，地鐵、有軌電車與公車加上[[葡萄牙铁路|葡萄牙鐵路]]的{{Tsl|pt|CP Urbanos de Lisboa|里斯本城市鐵路}}票價10.7歐元。單程票可以在{{Tsl|en|Lisbon metropolitan area|里斯本都會區}}內所有區域使用，無論距離長短。<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=Buy ML|url=https://www.metrolisboa.pt/en/buy/|access-date=2022-02-08|work=Metropolitano de Lisboa, EPE - English|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122002636/https://www.metrolisboa.pt/en/buy/|archive-date=2022-01-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

定期票以月為單位發售，定期票的售價依據使用範圍有差異，2004年開始里斯本引入分區票價，2019年里斯本更改分區方式，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sobre os novos passes|url=http://www.aml.pt/index.php?cMILID=SUS5C743299BA9B1&cMILL=3&mIID=SUS5C743261A63E4&mIN=sobre&mILA=&cMILID1=SUS5787A25518AED&mIID1=3&mIN1=Mobilidade%20e%20transportes&cMILID2=SUS5C7431770397C&mIID2=SUS5C743115D5991&mIN2=novos%20passes&cMILID3=SUS5C743299BA9B1&mIID3=SUS5C743261A63E4&mIN3=sobre|access-date=2022-02-08|work=AML|language=pt|archive-date=2021-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108113413/https://www.aml.pt/index.php?cMILID=SUS5C743299BA9B1&cMILL=3&mIID=SUS5C743261A63E4&mIN=sobre&mILA=&cMILID1=SUS5787A25518AED&mIID1=3&mIN1=Mobilidade%20e%20transportes&cMILID2=SUS5C7431770397C&mIID2=SUS5C743115D5991&mIN2=novos%20passes&cMILID3=SUS5C743299BA9B1&mIID3=SUS5C743261A63E4&mIN3=sobre|dead-url=no}}</ref>目前里斯本都會區被分為18個票價分區，里斯本地鐵經過其中3個，如果僅在某一區域往來，可購買單區域的定期票，每月30歐元，多區域定期票則可以往來2個以上的票價分區，價格為每月40歐元，未滿12歲的兒童免費，65歲以上長者每月20歐元。<ref name=":3" />

== 未來計畫 ==
目前里斯本地鐵的路網即將動工的計畫是連接黄线的拉托站，與綠線的索德雷碼頭車站，原計畫編入黃線營運<ref>{{Cite web|title=Expansão do metro em Lisboa vai custar 215 milhões|url=https://www.publico.pt/2016/12/15/economia/noticia/expansao-do-metro-de-lisboa-vai-custar-2015-milhoes-2021-1754815|access-date=2022-02-10|date=2016-12-15|work=PÚBLICO|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095719/https://www.publico.pt/2016/12/15/economia/noticia/expansao-do-metro-de-lisboa-vai-custar-2015-milhoes-2021-1754815|archive-date=2020-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但是目前的計畫改為由綠線營運，原本屬於黃線的拉托站大坎波站改由綠線行駛，使綠線呈[[環狀線|環狀]]運營，黃線僅剩大坎波站以北的郊區部分，和從綠線獲得的大坎波站至泰萊拉斯站，里斯本計畫於2024年開通該路段，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tribunal de Contas dá "luz verde" à expansão do Metro de Lisboa - Renascença|url=https://rr.sapo.pt/noticia/pais/2021/02/15/tribunal-de-contas-da-luz-verde-a-expansao-do-metro-de-lisboa/226808/|access-date=2022-02-10|date=2021-02-15|work=Rádio Renascença|language=pt}}</ref>但計畫遭到許多批評，包括：截短黃線使郊區民眾無法直接抵達市中心、環線並非理想的圓形，無法發揮環線作用。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Cidadãos contra fim da Linha Amarela do Metro criticam início obra da 'Circular'|url=https://www.jornaldenegocios.pt/empresas/transportes/detalhe/cidadaos-contra-fim-da-linha-amarela-do-metro-criticam-inicio-obra-da-circular|access-date=2022-02-10|work=www.jornaldenegocios.pt|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414235243/https://www.jornaldenegocios.pt/empresas/transportes/detalhe/cidadaos-contra-fim-da-linha-amarela-do-metro-criticam-inicio-obra-da-circular|archive-date=2021-04-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Linha em círculo? Ou em laço? Dar prioridade a Alcântara? Expansão do Metro de Lisboa volta a dividir|url=https://lisboaparapessoas.pt/2021/11/19/metro-lisboa-expansao-linha-circular-camara-governo-pcp-moedas/|access-date=2022-02-10|date=2021-11-19|work=Lisboa Para Pessoas|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119223137/https://lisboaparapessoas.pt/2021/11/19/metro-lisboa-expansao-linha-circular-camara-governo-pcp-moedas/|archive-date=2021-11-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>

除了環線計畫外，里斯本地鐵的路網擴張計畫還包括：紅線向南延伸至{{Tsl|pt|Estação Ferroviária de Alcântara-Mar|阿爾坎塔拉馬爾車站}}、黃線終點奧迪韋拉什站至里斯本郊區[[洛里什|洛里什]]的[[輕軌運輸系統|輕軌]]、以及新建泰萊拉斯站至本菲卡，並由黃線營運<ref>{{Cite web|title=O que já se sabe sobre a expansão do Metro de Lisboa para além da Linha Circular|url=https://lisboaparapessoas.pt/2021/04/20/metro-lisboa-expansao-linha-vermelha/|access-date=2022-02-10|date=2021-04-20|work=Lisboa Para Pessoas|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210705103912/https://lisboaparapessoas.pt/2021/04/20/metro-lisboa-expansao-linha-vermelha/|archive-date=2021-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了路網擴張之外，ML計畫將增購42 節配備自動列車控制系統的車廂。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Metro investe 114,5 M em sistema de sinalização na aquisição de 42 carruagens|url=https://www.metrolisboa.pt/institucional/2020/01/24/metro-investe-1145-m-em-sistema-de-sinalizacao-na-aquisicao-de-42-carruagens/|access-date=2022-02-10|date=2020-01-24|work=Site do Metropolitano de Lisboa, EPE - Empresa|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008214249/https://www.metrolisboa.pt/institucional/2020/01/24/metro-investe-1145-m-em-sistema-de-sinalizacao-na-aquisicao-de-42-carruagens/|archive-date=2021-10-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

